<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Restaurant Approved</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f5f5f5;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background:#f5f5f5;padding:40px 0;">
    <tr>
        <td align="center">

            <table role="presentation" width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"
                   style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;">

                <tr>
                    <td style="background:#22c55e;padding:24px;text-align:center;">
                        <h1 style="margin:0;color:#ffffff;font-size:28px;">
                            🎉 Restaurant Approved
                        </h1>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:40px;color:#333333;">

                        <p style="font-size:18px;margin-top:0;">
                            Hello <strong>{{ owner_name }}</strong>,
                        </p>

                        <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;">
                            Congratulations!
                        </p>

                        <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;">
                            Your restaurant
                            <strong>{{ restaurant_name }}</strong>
                            has been successfully approved by the FoodRush team.
                        </p>

                        <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;">
                            You can now:
                        </p>

                        <ul style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;">
                            <li>Add and manage your menu.</li>
                            <li>Receive customer orders.</li>
                            <li>Grow your business on FoodRush.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;">
                            We're excited to have you as one of our restaurant partners.
                        </p>

                        <p style="margin-top:40px;">
                            Best regards,<br/>
                            <strong>FoodRush Team</strong>
                        </p>

                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:20px;text-align:center;background:#f8f8f8;color:#888;font-size:12px;">
                        © 2026 FoodRush. All rights reserved.
                    </td>
                </tr>

            </table>

        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>